-based	employee	reporting	system.	\n•	HRMS	Portal	-	Java-based	payroll	and	payslip	generation	system.	\n	\nPersonal	Information	\nHobbies:	Travelling,	Cooking,	Playing	Guitar,	Solving	puzzles	(e.g.,	Rubik’s	cube)	\nLanguages	Known:	English,	Hindi,	Tel u gu ,	Marathi','done',0,'2026-05-14 20:35:21','2026-05-14 21:04:17',NULL),(3,1,'uploads/resumes/resume_1_1778792657508.pdf','Nachiketh M Desai - Resume.pdf',59602,'application/pdf','\n\n15/05/26, 02:34Nachiketh M Desai - Resume\nPage 1 of 3file:///Users/nachikethdesai/resume.html\nNACHIKETH M DESAI\n [PHONE REDACTED] |  [EMAIL REDACTED]\n Date of Birth: 25 April 2000\nA passionate and detail-oriented Electronics and Communication Engineer with a strong focus\non  Embedded Systems,  IoT,  and  hardware  integration.  Experienced  in  developing  real-time\nautomation  solutions  using microcontrollers,  NVIDIA  Jetson  Boards,  Raspberry  Pi,  and\nactuator-based systems. Skilled in wireless communication, sensor interfacing, and embedded\nhardware-software  integration.  Looking  to  contribute  to innovative,  software  and  hardware-\ndriven projects.\nWORK EXPERIENCE\nIoT Lead\nMAY 2025 - Present\nCognolabs Systems Private Limited\nLeading Edge AI projects including image recognition, video surveillance, and AI-based\ninventory systems.\nDevOps Engineer Trainee\nFEB 2025 - APR 2025\nITS Planners & Engineers Pvt Ltd\nManaged Raspberry Pi-based traffic signal systems and large-scale HTMS projects.\nMonitored servers across India, used Docker, Redis, and databases for system integration.\nL2 - Project Engineer\nNOV 2021 - AUG 2024\nWipro Limited\nGenerated MPLS configurations, managed VPN connectivity, and was promoted as SPOC for\nAPAC and RAM regions.\nResearch Intern\nDEC 2019\n\n15/05/26, 02:34Nachiketh M Desai - Resume\nPage 2 of 3file:///Users/nachikethdesai/resume.html\nAdministrative Staff College of India\nContributed to EV policy enhancement project in Telangana.\nSummer Intern\nJUN 2019\nECIL\nBuilt an IoT-